<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
  <title>imPD — 흩어진 내 일, 하나의 주소로 (30초 소개)</title>
  <meta name="description" content="1인 사업가를 위한 올인원 비즈니스 페이지. 흩어진 내 일을 하나의 주소로 모으세요.">

  <!-- OG 메타 (카톡/슬랙/SNS 썸네일) -->
  <meta property="og:type" content="video.other">
  <meta property="og:title" content="imPD — 흩어진 내 일, 하나의 주소로">
  <meta property="og:description" content="1인 사업가의 페이지 운영 OS. 5분이면 켜집니다.">
  <meta property="og:url" content="<%= @share_url %>">
  <meta property="og:image" content="<%= request.protocol + request.host_with_port + @poster_url %>">
  <meta property="og:video" content="<%= request.protocol + request.host_with_port + @video_url %>">
  <meta property="og:video:type" content="video/mp4">
  <meta property="og:video:width" content="1920">
  <meta property="og:video:height" content="1080">
  <meta name="twitter:card" content="summary_large_image">
  <meta name="twitter:title" content="imPD — 흩어진 내 일, 하나의 주소로">
  <meta name="twitter:image" content="<%= request.protocol + request.host_with_port + @poster_url %>">

  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Inter:wght@400;500;600;700;800&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

  <style>
    :root {
      --ink: #0f172a;
      --hero: #00A1E0;
      --paper: #efece4;
      --muted: rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.55);
    }
    * { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: "Inter", -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Pretendard Variable", sans-serif;
      background: var(--paper);
      color: var(--ink);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      align-items: center;
      padding: 48px 24px;
    }

    .brand {
      font-size: 28px; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    }
    .brand .dot { color: var(--hero); }

    .eyebrow {
      font-family: ui-monospace, "SF Mono", monospace;
      font-size: 11px; letter-spacing: 0.2em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--hero);
      margin-top: 24px;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(32px, 5vw, 54px);
      font-weight: 800;
      letter-spacing: -0.03em;
      line-height: 1.05;
      margin-top: 10px;
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 820px;
    }

    .video-wrap {
      width: 100%;
      max-width: 960px;
      margin-top: 36px;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: #000;
      box-shadow: 0 30px 80px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.18), 0 0 0 1px rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.08);
      aspect-ratio: 16 / 9;
    }
    .video-wrap video {
      width: 100%; height: 100%;
      display: block;
    }

    .actions {
      display: flex; gap: 12px; flex-wrap: wrap;
      margin-top: 28px;
      justify-content: center;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: 8px;
      padding: 12px 22px;
      font-family: inherit; font-size: 14px; font-weight: 600;
      letter-spacing: -0.01em;
      border-radius: 10px;
      cursor: pointer; border: 1px solid var(--ink);
      background: transparent; color: var(--ink);
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all .15s;
    }
    .btn:hover { background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper); }
    .btn.primary {
      background: var(--hero);
      border-color: var(--hero);
      color: #05161f;
      box-shadow: 0 0 30px rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.35);
    }
    .btn.primary:hover { background: #0081b8; border-color: #0081b8; color: #fff; }

    .share-url {
      margin-top: 18px;
      font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
      font-size: 12px; color: var(--muted);
      padding: 8px 14px;
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid rgba(15, 23, 42, 0.12);
      border-radius: 8px;
      user-select: all;
    }

    .downloads {
      margin-top: 24px;
      display: flex; gap: 14px; flex-wrap: wrap;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
    .downloads a { color: var(--muted); text-decoration: underline; }
    .downloads a:hover { color: var(--ink); }

    .tagline {
      margin-top: 48px;
      font-size: 13px;
      font-family: ui-monospace, monospace;
      letter-spacing: 0.15em; text-transform: uppercase;
      color: var(--muted);
    }

    .flash {
      position: fixed; top: 20px; left: 50%; transform: translateX(-50%);
      padding: 10px 18px;
      background: var(--ink); color: var(--paper);
      border-radius: 999px;
      font-size: 13px;
      opacity: 0; pointer-events: none;
      transition: opacity .2s;
    }
    .flash.show { opacity: 1; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="brand">imPD<span class="dot">.</span></div>
  <p class="eyebrow">§ PROMO · 00:30</p>
  <h1>흩어진 내 일,<br>하나의 주소로.</h1>

  <div class="video-wrap">
    <video
      src="<%= @video_url %>"
      poster="<%= @poster_url %>"
      controls
      playsinline
      preload="metadata">
      영상을 재생할 수 없습니다. <a href="<%= @video_url %>">직접 다운로드</a>해 주세요.
    </video>
  </div>

  <div class="actions">
    <a class="btn primary" href="/auth/signup">내 페이지 만들기 →</a>
    <button class="btn" type="button" onclick="copyLink()">🔗 링크 복사</button>
    <a class="btn" href="<%= @video_url %>" download="impd-promo.mp4">⬇ mp4 다운로드</a>
    <a class="btn" href="/promo">▶ 라이브 재생(HTML)</a>
  </div>

  <p class="share-url" id="shareUrl"><%= @share_url %></p>

  <p class="tagline">EST. 2026 · SEOUL · imPD.townin.net</p>

  <div class="flash" id="flash">링크가 복사되었습니다</div>

  <script>
    function copyLink() {
      const url = document.getElementById('shareUrl').textContent.trim();
      navigator.clipboard.writeText(url).then(() => {
        const flash = document.getElementById('flash');
        flash.classList.add('show');
        setTimeout(() => flash.classList.remove('show'), 1800);
      });
    }
  </script>
</body>
</html>
